channel.title: De-FaultScape 562 server Now Online 24/7 Dedicated Server/Custom Shops and MORE
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/snOiXB5.png[/img][/center] [center] De-FaultScape has just launched!! Version: 562 Currently being maintained by headyGains and Fullmetal140. Recruiting Developers/Mods if interested apply on our [url=http://www.defaultrs.betaboard.net]Forums[/url]. We currently have a Downloadable 1-click play client, and a Web-Client (mods have to be made to your java cp to use) we have a tutorial in our new user section to do this. We are just starting out in RSPS server development, and are very much in need of people to test our server! Based on Goudont's Final Release with Aviboss. Thank you guys for such an awesome source.
Here are some Pics![/center] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/Enj3uP9.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/aMVnMtJ.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/Tndn2Rk.png[/img]
In all honesty I'm really short-selling the quality of this server, constant updates and development (I've only been at this a few days lol) Looking to dedicating the next few years to this project. So anyone who would like to have a good time competitive and casual alike please join us at [url=http://www.defaultrs.betaboard.net]De-FaultScape[/url]
Play ON!!
